data.description: This is a 3 bedroom, 2 bath ranch style home with an open floor plan on a walkout lot. The efficient kitchen features an island & pantry & has plenty of cabinets and workspace whether you like to cook or entertain. Quartz counter tops, LVP flooring through Living room, kitchen and entry along with all the baths. Vaulted ceilings in the living room & dining room. The primary bedroom features a tray ceiling, master bath & walk in closet. Basement is partially finished adding another bedroom and walk in closet. Yard is completed fenced.
